General Information
===================

This is LibThai version 0.1.0. LibThai is a library which includes
Thai language support routines, such as :

  - Thai character set support: TIS 620, ISO/IEC 10646
  - Thai character properties
  - Thai string manipulators
  - Thai string collation
  - Thai word breaking
  - Thai input method
  - Thai output method

The official web site is:
  http://linux.thai.net/libthai

Installation
============

See the file 'INSTALL'.

